    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Mechanisms in clocks and watches that measure beats and control the speed of the going trains thus controling the indication of the passage of time.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
